\b listen-osc_writeArrayConfig.py
\b0 ,  is available in 
\b triad_openvr-master_DM
\b0 , for creating an array configuration at the same time as the calibration process. The scripts can be executed by running, eg,  \'91python tracker_test_DM_measureArray.py\'92 in a console window.
